<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV4">
<l>mūṉṟumuppat tāṟiṉōṭo raintumaintu maintumāy</l>
<l>mūṉṟumūrtti yākimūṉṟu mūṉṟumūṉṟu mūṉṟumāyt</l>
<l>tōṉṟucōti mūṉṟumāyt tuḷakkamil viḷakkamāy</l>
<l>ēṉṟeṉāvi yuḷpukunta teṉkolōvem mīcaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being [the lord of] the thirty-three [consonants];</l>
<l rend="indent">the five [plus] five [plus] one [vowels] along with the five [syllables],</l>
<l>being the three forms [of the three Vedas],</l>
<l>being [praised by the dvādaśākṣarī mantra with] three [plus] three,</l>
<l>[plus] three, [plus] three [syllables], being the three [syllable-lit] light,</l>
<l>being the undiminishing light, our supreme Lord!</l>
<l rend="indent">What for did You accept [me] and enter my soul?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
